info.name: Spl Chicken Zafrani Berry Pulao
info.description: Dive into the royal flavors of spl chicken zafrani berry pulao, a fusion masterpiece where succulent chicken meets fragrant saffron rice and tangy berries. Let each bite transport you to a regal feast, celebrating a symphony of tastes and textures in this exquisite dish. Accompanied with onions and thick raita. A true delight for all the biryani lovers

info.name: Kaju Kheema Zafrani Berry Pulao
info.description: Savor the sumptuous kaju kheema zafrani berry pulao, a gourmet blend where rich minced chicken and crunchy cashews meet aromatic saffron rice and tangy berries. Dive into this majestic dish, offering a flavorful celebration that's both regal and utterly delectable. Accompanied with onions and thick raita. A true delight for all the biryani lovers

info.name: Malai Chicken Zafrani Berry Pulao
info.description: Relish the luxurious fusion of malai chicken zafrani berry pulao, where creamy chicken morsels are adorned with fragrant saffron rice and zesty berries. This exquisite creation promises a culinary journey of velvety textures and aromatic delights with every bite. Accompanied with onions and thick raita. A true delight for all the biryani lovers

info.name: Prawns Roast Zafrani Berry Pulao
info.description: Dive deep into the flavors of prawns roast zafrani berry pulao, where succulent roasted prawns seamlessly blend with aromatic saffron and tangy berries. Experience this maritime delight, marrying the richness of the sea with the opulence of a royal pulao. Accompanied with onions and thick raita. A true delight for all the biryani lovers

info.name: Spl Paneer Zafrani Berry Pulao
info.description: Indulge in the spl paneer zafrani berry pulao, a vegetarian delight where soft paneer cubes are accentuated with fragrant saffron rice and tangy berries. Experience this special dish, a symphony of rich flavors and textures that promises an unforgettable culinary journey.  accompanied with onions and thick raita. A true delight for all the biryani lovers

info.name: Spl Manchurian Zafrani Berry Pualo
info.description: Venture into the fusion realm with spl manchurian zafrani berry pulao, a culinary twist where spicy manchurian balls unite with fragrant saffron rice and vibrant berries. Relish this special concoction, blending the zesty flavors of indo-chinese with the royal touch of zafrani pulao. Accompanied with onions and thick raita. A true delight for all the biryani lovers
